Changes:
 jm-util (0.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   [ Jan Matějka ]
   * rf(versionator): simplify regex
   * fx(#build): make install-home - make i_bin_dir if missing
   * ft(#build): general support to build and install zsh completions
   * fx(jm-alias#build): make check runs dram_check
   * ft(oci#build): rewrite gitdirs only for debuild
   * fx(oci#build): overlays only for debuild
   * ft(oci/Containerfile#build): add libargparse-dev for jm-alias
   * ft(jm-alias): add --show-aliases
   * ft(jm-alias): add --compdef
   * ft(jm-alias): generate compdef files
   * fx(GNUmakefile#build): PHONY: packages mark
   * fx(versionator): always generate changelog (not just without -d)
   * fx(#build): building dev debian packages
